WEBVTT

01:37.100 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.520 --> 01:48.750
[Episode 15: Red beans are sweet and sour in taste and neutral in nature. They promote urination, reduce swelling, clear toxins, and expel pus.]

02:36.010 --> 02:38.079
What's wrong? You're scared to see me?

02:41.560 --> 02:42.590
Why are you scared?

02:44.050 --> 02:46.210
Because my mom told me

02:46.240 --> 02:49.680
to behave well my first time here

02:50.880 --> 02:52.280
and not to be a nuisance.

02:56.880 --> 02:58.070
I have something for you.

03:06.200 --> 03:07.510
Take it.

03:08.830 --> 03:10.160
When I came back,

03:10.180 --> 03:11.570
I forgot to buy you a gift.

03:12.800 --> 03:13.800
So take this lucky money

03:13.800 --> 03:15.240
and buy yourself something you like.

03:15.430 --> 03:16.640
Consider it my gift to you.

03:19.079 --> 03:20.280
Thank you, Dr. He.

03:22.829 --> 03:23.920
You're such a good boy.

03:24.470 --> 03:25.880
Everyone likes you.

03:28.400 --> 03:29.360
How long are you staying?

03:30.500 --> 03:32.150
About three more days.

03:32.590 --> 03:33.590
Are you leaving?

03:34.690 --> 03:35.730
I need to go back to work.

03:35.760 --> 03:36.510
So I'll be leaving.

03:37.060 --> 03:39.470
Have fun here with the other kids.

03:41.500 --> 03:42.230
I'm leaving.

03:43.590 --> 03:44.590
Bye-bye, Dr. He.

03:44.980 --> 03:45.770
Bye-bye.

03:58.200 --> 03:59.170
Go.

04:00.270 --> 04:01.280
Go.

04:09.680 --> 04:10.710
Everything's packed?

04:14.960 --> 04:16.200
Be safe on the road.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.990
I drank a bit too much last night.

04:24.110 --> 04:25.750
Don't take what I said to heart.

04:27.470 --> 04:28.270
I know.

04:28.990 --> 04:30.400
People are honest when they're drunk.

04:37.720 --> 04:38.430
Alright.

04:39.200 --> 04:41.530
I'll be going then.

04:42.880 --> 04:43.630
Okay.

05:27.860 --> 05:30.100
I'm back. I have something for you.

05:36.690 --> 05:38.330
I was just about to go downstairs for a walk.

05:38.640 --> 05:40.990
Let's meet at the park, shall we?

06:01.130 --> 06:01.860
These are for you.

06:08.080 --> 06:08.670
Oh, right.

06:10.270 --> 06:10.910
And this too.

06:15.310 --> 06:16.640
Xiangya told me everything.

06:17.240 --> 06:19.530
I think you really need this right now.

06:24.030 --> 06:26.270
Actually, Xifan's love life

06:26.570 --> 06:27.570
is pretty simple.

06:28.810 --> 06:31.300
She only had a seven-year relationship with her first love.

06:31.750 --> 06:32.800
They broke up last year.

06:33.680 --> 06:35.240
They lived in different cities for a long time.

06:36.000 --> 06:38.510
Towards the end, she was in a really bad state.

06:39.870 --> 06:42.140
She's scared of getting hurt again.

06:45.240 --> 06:47.720
All blockages build up over time.

06:48.190 --> 06:49.280
When there's stagnation, there's pain.

06:49.970 --> 06:51.260
Red beans help

06:51.290 --> 06:53.360
clear stagnation and heal sores.

06:53.830 --> 06:55.510
They can also help improve your mood.

07:07.750 --> 07:08.310
What's wrong?

07:13.680 --> 07:15.120
I'm just thinking…

07:18.270 --> 07:19.780
Why aren't you angry?

07:25.600 --> 07:26.750
Maybe because

07:27.310 --> 07:29.950
I've been through something similar.

07:30.390 --> 07:32.830
So I can relate.

07:33.530 --> 07:35.760
After I was dumped,

07:35.790 --> 07:37.680
I was self-destructive for a while.

07:38.870 --> 07:41.510
During that period, I ate medicinal food every day

07:41.720 --> 07:42.750
for more than a year.

07:43.560 --> 07:44.920
It worked pretty well.

07:46.390 --> 07:47.830
But later, I realized that

07:48.310 --> 07:49.950
while medicinal food does help,

07:50.360 --> 07:51.630
the most important thing

07:51.920 --> 07:53.159
is to get back

07:53.159 --> 07:55.130
to a normal routine with regular meals.

07:57.830 --> 08:00.160
So it's the same for you.

08:01.000 --> 08:02.170
Don't think you're not good enough.

08:02.310 --> 08:04.040
Don't think you have no value.

08:04.600 --> 08:06.480
You're just hurt

08:06.480 --> 08:07.600
by a bad relationship.

08:09.480 --> 08:10.510
Love yourself

08:10.800 --> 08:13.100
and live well. That's the most important thing.

08:16.720 --> 08:19.560
You can take your time with everything else.

08:33.039 --> 08:33.850
That said,

08:36.200 --> 08:37.600
if possible,

08:39.000 --> 08:40.150
I do hope

08:40.480 --> 08:41.960
you can heal a little faster.

08:56.140 --> 09:02.820
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

09:03.040 --> 09:08.160
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

09:09.740 --> 09:15.660
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

09:11.600 --> 09:13.320
Next time you have red beans,

09:13.320 --> 09:14.390
send me a photo.

09:16.630 --> 09:24.340
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

09:42.510 --> 09:43.630
Here, have some tea.

09:48.390 --> 09:50.630
You didn't argue with him when you went back for the Spring Festival, did you?

09:51.270 --> 09:53.240
No. He barely had time for me.

09:57.750 --> 09:59.750
He found himself a girlfriend.

10:00.270 --> 10:01.750
She seems nice,

10:02.180 --> 10:04.380
and they get along fine.

10:19.310 --> 10:21.270
Your mom's been gone for so long.

10:22.120 --> 10:24.630
Some things are better left in the past.

10:25.480 --> 10:26.440
I've let it go.

10:26.440 --> 10:28.060
Why can't you?

10:29.910 --> 10:31.600
At your dad's age,

10:31.600 --> 10:34.790
it's understandable for him to find someone to share his life with.

10:36.000 --> 10:37.450
Just let him be.

10:40.080 --> 10:40.840
I know.

10:43.200 --> 10:44.030
How about this?

10:44.320 --> 10:45.700
I'll come here every year

10:45.840 --> 10:47.960
to celebrate the Spring Festival with you two.

10:48.790 --> 10:50.480
It's not like he needs me there anyway.

10:51.360 --> 10:52.830
Alright, suit yourself.

10:54.870 --> 10:55.720
By the way,

10:56.200 --> 10:57.360
Fang

10:57.630 --> 11:01.510
told me she wants to change her field of study for her PhD.

11:01.750 --> 11:03.080
Do you know why?

11:07.840 --> 11:09.150
That's what she told you?

11:11.630 --> 11:14.510
Did you not mentor her properly during her internship?

11:15.150 --> 11:17.790
She's dedicated and hardworking.

11:18.080 --> 11:19.510
She has a promising future.

11:20.150 --> 11:21.840
Did you not guide her well?

11:22.240 --> 11:22.870
I…

11:24.440 --> 11:25.360
Look at you.

11:25.750 --> 11:26.910
You haven't even asked her yourself,

11:26.910 --> 11:28.030
and you don't know the reason,

11:28.030 --> 11:29.320
yet you're already blaming me.

11:30.630 --> 11:31.870
I'm not blaming you.

11:31.870 --> 11:32.550
I just don't want

11:32.550 --> 11:34.550
her talent to be wasted.

11:35.720 --> 11:36.960
Don't worry. It won't be.

11:38.720 --> 11:39.910
She must have

11:40.240 --> 11:41.630
her own reasons for this decision.

11:42.670 --> 11:44.080
But since it concerns her future,

11:44.320 --> 11:46.200
you should think it over for her.

11:46.780 --> 11:48.330
You don't need to remind me of that.

11:57.870 --> 11:59.080
Cheers!

11:59.870 --> 12:01.790
Today, we're gathered here

12:01.790 --> 12:03.030
to celebrate

12:03.030 --> 12:04.540
that my supplementary application materials

12:04.570 --> 12:05.500
have been approved.

12:05.720 --> 12:06.480
Congratulations.

12:06.480 --> 12:08.960
Congratulations on your dream coming true.

12:09.240 --> 12:09.910
Thank you.

12:11.030 --> 12:11.630
By the way,

12:12.030 --> 12:12.910
when does the semester start?

12:13.150 --> 12:15.480
I remember overseas programs usually begin in February.

12:16.150 --> 12:17.630
February or October.

12:18.270 --> 12:20.550
If it's February, that's coming up soon.

12:20.550 --> 12:22.360
You better start preparing now,

12:22.360 --> 12:23.910
or you might not have time to get your visa.

12:26.200 --> 12:27.840
Actually, today,

12:27.840 --> 12:29.910
I want to ask you two for advice on something.

12:30.830 --> 12:31.530
Go ahead.

12:32.200 --> 12:33.510
I want to go in October.

12:34.550 --> 12:36.960
The college allows students to secure their admission

12:36.960 --> 12:38.410
as long as they pay the tuition in advance.

12:38.510 --> 12:39.890
So I have two options now:

12:40.030 --> 12:41.840
February or October.

12:42.670 --> 12:44.270
Why wait until October?

12:44.270 --> 12:45.240
Go early and come back early.

12:45.960 --> 12:47.390
There are two reasons.

12:47.600 --> 12:48.270
First,

12:48.270 --> 12:50.390
I've only just saved enough for tuition.

12:50.390 --> 12:51.720
I'm still a bit short on living expenses,

12:52.000 --> 12:54.440
so I think I'll work a little longer and save up more.

12:54.870 --> 12:57.120
Can't your parents help out a bit?

12:58.790 --> 13:00.510
I don't want to ask them for help.

13:00.720 --> 13:01.790
They're both in their fifties now

13:01.790 --> 13:02.870
and will retire soon.

13:02.870 --> 13:04.630
Besides, studying abroad

13:04.630 --> 13:06.270
was my decision in the first place.

13:08.440 --> 13:09.150
And the other reason?

13:11.080 --> 13:12.550
Well,

13:12.790 --> 13:15.550
it's been six and a half years since I joined Gunan Huating Hotel.

13:15.550 --> 13:17.510
If I leave in October,

13:17.510 --> 13:19.540
it'll be seven years,

13:19.690 --> 13:21.750
and I'll have worked for exactly one year

13:21.750 --> 13:23.000
as the front office manager.

13:23.390 --> 13:24.270
That way,

13:24.270 --> 13:25.960
my resume will look more complete.

13:27.910 --> 13:29.720
After all that explanation,

13:29.720 --> 13:31.320
it doesn't seem

13:31.320 --> 13:33.030
to have anything to do with Dr. He.

13:33.030 --> 13:35.200
Are you sure it has nothing to do with Dr. He?

13:42.910 --> 13:44.870
Congratulations on getting your offer!

13:44.870 --> 13:46.360
Cheers!

13:50.600 --> 13:51.720
It tastes so good.

13:53.630 --> 13:54.600
Eat up.

13:55.870 --> 13:56.530
Oh, right.

13:57.200 --> 14:00.360
I want to run something by you two.

14:00.360 --> 14:01.120
Go ahead.

14:02.960 --> 14:06.630
I want to go abroad in October,

14:06.910 --> 14:09.200
which means I'll leave in October

14:09.200 --> 14:11.240
and come back next August.

14:11.440 --> 14:11.960
Is that okay?

14:13.720 --> 14:14.480
Of course.

14:15.320 --> 14:16.440
I have no objections.

14:17.000 --> 14:17.630
That way,

14:17.630 --> 14:18.760
you'll have plenty of time

14:18.960 --> 14:20.480
and won't have to worry about your visa and such.

14:21.160 --> 14:22.710
Right. But

14:22.790 --> 14:24.150
when you come back from abroad,

14:24.360 --> 14:25.600
you'll be 29.

14:25.870 --> 14:27.670
I'll be 29 sooner or later anyway.

14:28.510 --> 14:29.730
We're celebrating.

14:30.550 --> 14:31.750
I'll have another drink.

14:33.630 --> 14:34.150
Come on.

14:34.600 --> 14:35.390
Let's have another toast.

14:35.630 --> 14:36.580
Let's clink glasses again.

14:36.750 --> 14:37.720
Cheers!

14:37.720 --> 14:38.370
Congratulations.

14:42.070 --> 14:43.520
It's so good.

14:44.650 --> 14:46.240
-I'd like a little more.
-Eat up.

14:49.750 --> 14:51.550
Great news.

14:52.200 --> 14:53.320
My parents have agreed

14:53.320 --> 14:55.320
to my going abroad in October.

14:56.150 --> 14:58.510
That's great. Everything is going smoothly.

14:58.750 --> 14:59.750
It's a good sign.

15:04.710 --> 15:05.270
By the way,

15:05.990 --> 15:08.590
make sure to inform everyone who needs to know.

15:10.510 --> 15:11.440
Got it.

15:12.890 --> 15:13.720
That's it.

15:13.720 --> 15:14.600
Don't drag it out.

15:14.870 --> 15:15.440
Bye-bye.

15:16.630 --> 15:17.390
Bye-bye.

15:24.790 --> 15:26.630
How should I tell him?

15:27.600 --> 15:29.720
If I say I won't leave until October,

15:30.200 --> 15:32.270
will it sound like I'm implying something?

15:42.670 --> 15:43.870
Dr. He.

15:46.870 --> 15:47.790
I…

16:36.750 --> 16:37.650
Dr. He,

16:37.910 --> 16:39.150
I got my offer.

16:39.150 --> 16:40.900
This October, I will...

16:59.710 --> 17:02.710
How do I even bring this up?

17:08.790 --> 17:09.790
No.

17:16.280 --> 17:20.520
[Typing…]

17:30.390 --> 17:32.270
What does he want to say?

18:21.970 --> 18:23.250
Thank you for today.

18:23.280 --> 18:25.000
If anything else comes up, I'll contact you again.

18:25.060 --> 18:25.540
Alright.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.070
Thank you.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.600
Ms. Liu.

18:39.160 --> 18:42.020
Why don't we go to the hospital for a check-up?

18:42.510 --> 18:45.310
The staff happened to be cleaning the courtyard today.

18:45.310 --> 18:46.200
What if next time

18:46.200 --> 18:47.850
you're alone in the room?

18:47.960 --> 18:49.510
I'm quite worried.

18:53.200 --> 18:55.400
My cough and chest tightness

18:55.750 --> 18:57.510
are the after-effects

18:57.510 --> 18:59.440
of my lung cancer treatment overseas years ago.

19:00.790 --> 19:02.400
Going to the hospital again

19:02.680 --> 19:04.070
means a whole ordeal—

19:04.070 --> 19:07.440
blood transfusions, hospital stays, and surgery.

19:07.750 --> 19:08.880
I really don't want

19:08.900 --> 19:10.820
to go through all that again.

19:16.000 --> 19:18.560
Ms. Liu, I know a TCM physician

19:18.720 --> 19:19.960
who specializes in oncology.

19:20.060 --> 19:21.710
Maybe he can help you.

19:22.220 --> 19:23.590
He once told me

19:23.590 --> 19:25.510
that TCM treatments are mostly

19:25.510 --> 19:28.360
herbal medicine, acupuncture, moxibustion, and cupping.

19:28.680 --> 19:30.200
They don't sound too overwhelming.

19:30.200 --> 19:31.300
You could at least check it out.

19:31.320 --> 19:33.710
Even if he can't cure you,

19:33.790 --> 19:34.880
if he can ease the symptoms,

19:34.880 --> 19:35.960
wouldn't that still be a good thing?

19:36.070 --> 19:39.110
Does TCM help with the after-effects of radiation therapy?

19:39.480 --> 19:40.630
I'm not sure,

19:40.750 --> 19:42.270
but I can ask him for you.

19:45.550 --> 19:48.160
Alright, please do.

19:48.880 --> 19:49.880
No problem.

19:53.550 --> 19:54.480
Dr. He,

19:55.200 --> 19:58.160
can I ask you some questions?

20:08.750 --> 20:09.880
Take your medicine on time.

20:10.070 --> 20:10.680
Thank you.

20:41.270 --> 20:42.680
Sure, go ahead.

20:53.160 --> 20:55.440
There's a guest at our hotel

20:56.000 --> 20:58.220
who's in her seventies and had lung cancer before.

20:58.370 --> 21:00.040
She should be fully recovered now,

21:00.350 --> 21:02.480
but she often coughs and experiences chest tightness.

21:03.110 --> 21:04.920
Are they the after-effects of the surgery?

21:10.030 --> 21:10.790
It's possible.

21:11.510 --> 21:13.160
But since she had lung cancer before,

21:13.270 --> 21:14.480
the situation is quite complex.

21:15.110 --> 21:16.550
I need to see her in person

21:16.550 --> 21:17.540
to make a more specific assessment.

21:21.000 --> 21:21.640
Okay.

21:41.200 --> 21:42.240
But she's not willing

21:42.240 --> 21:44.440
to be hospitalized or undergo surgery.

21:44.830 --> 21:46.310
Would TCM be an option?

21:52.510 --> 21:53.000
Yes.

21:53.850 --> 21:55.140
Bring her to the hospital to see me.

21:55.270 --> 21:56.550
I see patients in the afternoon.

21:56.960 --> 21:57.920
Try to come early.

22:13.350 --> 22:13.960
Okay.

22:15.630 --> 22:18.600
I'll set up a time with her and let you know.

23:32.830 --> 23:33.640
Your medical records?

23:56.900 --> 24:00.080
♫Never know what to do♫

24:00.260 --> 24:03.580
♫In the times, I'm with you♫

24:07.550 --> 24:10.590
♫Never know what to say♫

24:10.880 --> 24:14.970
♫In the hours, I'm with you♫

24:11.590 --> 24:12.880
Wait outside for a moment.

24:13.270 --> 24:14.070
Alright.

24:18.260 --> 24:21.540
♫All I know, that it's true♫

24:23.890 --> 24:26.290
♫That it's true♫

24:48.790 --> 24:49.880
Alright, thank you.

24:51.030 --> 24:54.110
Ms. Liu, you're staying in Gunan Huating?

24:54.640 --> 24:56.350
Yes, it's been quite a while.

24:57.030 --> 24:59.580
Almost half a year now.

25:03.160 --> 25:04.510
From your medical records,

25:04.830 --> 25:06.400
you had radiation therapy the year before last.

25:06.730 --> 25:08.770
After your discharge, you've been having chest tightness, shortness of breath,

25:08.800 --> 25:10.280
and a cough, right?

25:11.590 --> 25:12.440
Is it serious?

25:14.480 --> 25:15.310
Not very.

25:15.790 --> 25:17.830
The cough gets worse

25:18.310 --> 25:20.200
when I don't get enough rest.

25:21.960 --> 25:23.880
Do you have a CT scan I can look at?

25:27.760 --> 25:28.600
I have it.

25:42.240 --> 25:43.310
This isn't a digital copy.

25:43.440 --> 25:44.480
It's just a photo of the scan.

25:48.750 --> 25:50.110
This won't do. It's not clear enough.

25:52.110 --> 25:54.700
Ms. Liu, I'll need you to get another CT scan.

25:56.180 --> 25:57.250
Another one?

25:57.820 --> 25:59.010
Since we're already here,

25:59.040 --> 26:00.410
we might as well get everything done in one go.

26:02.600 --> 26:03.420
Okay.

26:04.510 --> 26:05.270
I'll accompany you.

26:05.310 --> 26:05.990
No need.

26:06.240 --> 26:08.240
Fang, take Ms. Liu

26:08.240 --> 26:09.240
to get her CT scan done.

26:09.920 --> 26:10.640
No, no.

26:10.640 --> 26:11.750
I can go with her.

26:11.750 --> 26:14.400
No need. I'm worried you and Ms. Liu might get lost.

26:15.270 --> 26:15.850
Fang,

26:16.440 --> 26:17.480
go with Ms. Liu.

26:18.000 --> 26:18.590
Okay.

26:28.030 --> 26:28.680
Thank you.

26:28.680 --> 26:29.840
Ms. Liu, this way, please.

26:47.030 --> 26:48.590
It's been several weeks since your last follow-up visit.

26:49.640 --> 26:51.640
How have you been feeling lately?

26:56.270 --> 26:57.200
Pretty good.

27:03.240 --> 27:04.110
Let me check your pulse.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.640
How's your plan to study abroad coming along?

27:39.400 --> 27:40.440
The Spring Festival is over.

27:40.680 --> 27:41.790
Have you received your offer?

27:44.750 --> 27:47.000
I've received the offer.

27:50.000 --> 27:50.790
That's great news.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.350
Why didn't you tell me?

27:56.880 --> 28:00.240
What about your visa? Have you got it?

28:03.240 --> 28:04.590
Actually…

28:06.790 --> 28:08.880
I'm not leaving until October.

28:19.440 --> 28:21.110
You said February before.

28:21.110 --> 28:22.510
Why the sudden change?

28:25.750 --> 28:26.640
At that time…

28:28.070 --> 28:30.400
I didn't know I could choose the semester,

28:30.400 --> 28:31.400
so I…

28:57.400 --> 28:58.310
Dr. He.

29:00.720 --> 29:05.160
Is there anything else wrong with my health?

29:06.270 --> 29:07.640
Nothing major.

29:10.000 --> 29:11.270
It's just…

29:17.550 --> 29:19.030
Just what?

29:21.200 --> 29:22.790
Just that you're a bit heartless.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.000
Don't worry.

29:35.200 --> 29:36.750
Just drink some tangerine peel tea.

30:01.160 --> 30:03.440
Look, this is your medical record,

30:03.550 --> 30:04.590
and this is the prescription.

30:04.920 --> 30:06.160
Once the decoction is ready,

30:06.160 --> 30:08.350
it'll be delivered to the hotel.

30:08.350 --> 30:09.480
Okay.

30:10.000 --> 30:11.830
You'll take this decoction for a week

30:11.830 --> 30:13.400
and then come back for a follow-up visit.

30:13.790 --> 30:14.960
Next time you come,

30:14.960 --> 30:16.680
I suggest you try acupuncture.

30:16.960 --> 30:19.070
Based on my experience with TCM,

30:19.200 --> 30:21.680
acupuncture tends to work faster.

30:21.680 --> 30:22.790
I suggest you give it a try.

30:23.270 --> 30:24.070
Alright.

30:25.790 --> 30:28.160
Thanks for coming to the hospital with me today.

30:28.400 --> 30:30.640
Not at all. I'll call us a car.

30:30.640 --> 30:31.480
Okay.

30:33.680 --> 30:34.550
Shen.

30:35.110 --> 30:37.880
What's your relationship with Dr. He?

30:42.750 --> 30:43.830
We're just friends.

30:44.240 --> 30:45.200
I don't think so.

30:46.310 --> 30:47.790
I can tell—

30:48.350 --> 30:51.110
he's the "unhappy decision" you mentioned,

30:51.110 --> 30:51.750
right?

30:54.350 --> 30:56.400
I'm not trying to pry into your privacy.

30:57.160 --> 30:58.480
I just feel that

30:59.350 --> 31:01.240
he cares about you a lot.

31:04.270 --> 31:06.640
If you were truly certain about your decision,

31:06.640 --> 31:09.000
you wouldn't be so concerned about his feelings.

31:10.240 --> 31:11.750
There are things

31:13.110 --> 31:15.000
you don't have to admit,

31:15.510 --> 31:18.200
but your heart always knows the truth.

31:33.830 --> 31:35.110
Don't think you're not good enough.

31:35.110 --> 31:36.920
Don't think you have no value.

31:37.480 --> 31:39.310
You're just hurt

31:39.310 --> 31:40.590
by a bad relationship.

31:41.550 --> 31:43.200
If possible,

31:44.440 --> 31:47.400
I do hope you can heal a little faster.

32:39.420 --> 32:40.980
The red beans…

32:44.550 --> 32:46.200
Isn't it too early?

32:56.770 --> 32:58.160
Did you eat the red beans?

33:31.640 --> 33:35.770
[Message: Jiangzhou Local Food. Red beans…]

33:39.640 --> 33:40.920
She's still not up?

33:42.160 --> 33:43.510
I wonder if she ate them or not.

34:04.000 --> 34:06.030
I can tell you slept well last night.

34:06.030 --> 34:07.720
You look much better than you did the past couple of days.

34:10.230 --> 34:11.670
I made it according to your recipe.

34:12.000 --> 34:13.350
Black rice porridge with red beans and tangerine peels.

34:15.710 --> 34:16.670
It smells so good.

34:17.030 --> 34:19.480
Look at these red beans. They're really good.

34:19.670 --> 34:20.550
All plump.

34:20.550 --> 34:22.030
No impurities at all.

34:22.880 --> 34:24.710
And the best part? They come with

34:24.710 --> 34:25.710
cooking recipes.

34:25.710 --> 34:26.400
Yeah.

34:26.400 --> 34:27.320
That's great.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.880
Where is the shop? I'll check it out someday.

34:32.000 --> 34:34.280
I ran into the seller just outside our complex.

34:34.800 --> 34:36.150
He was a vendor

34:36.150 --> 34:38.000
wearing a white top

34:38.000 --> 34:39.400
and carrying a plastic bag.

34:40.070 --> 34:41.360
A street vendor?

34:43.590 --> 34:45.449
I'll take a walk outside the complex someday.

34:45.469 --> 34:46.719
Who knows? I might run into him.

34:56.280 --> 34:57.800
I plan to try every one

34:57.800 --> 34:59.670
of these recipes for you.

34:59.960 --> 35:00.960
Sounds good.

35:03.960 --> 35:04.880
Aren't you having some?

35:04.910 --> 35:05.800
I am, I am.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.360
Only half is left.

35:11.510 --> 35:12.440
A bit more sugar?

35:12.440 --> 35:13.110
Okay.

35:13.480 --> 35:14.190
It tastes better with some sugar.

35:27.800 --> 35:29.070
Homework.

35:53.880 --> 35:55.070
Full marks?

35:55.960 --> 35:57.400
Is this an exam?

36:50.390 --> 36:52.100
Alright. We have to say goodbye here.

36:52.440 --> 36:53.960
If anything comes up, contact me anytime.

36:55.520 --> 36:57.290
Remember to get a check-up every six months

36:57.320 --> 36:58.510
to prevent recurrence and metastasis.

36:58.800 --> 37:00.840
Don't skip it just because it's troublesome.

37:00.840 --> 37:02.150
Early detection, early treatment.

37:02.150 --> 37:02.840
Okay.

37:03.690 --> 37:04.810
Also,

37:04.920 --> 37:06.300
encourage him to do light exercise,

37:06.320 --> 37:07.680
but avoid intense workouts.

37:10.320 --> 37:12.030
My decoction formula strengthens the body, expels pathogens,

37:12.030 --> 37:12.910
and boosts immunity.

37:12.960 --> 37:13.960
Make sure to take it on time.

37:15.670 --> 37:16.480
Be good.

37:17.230 --> 37:18.550
Eat more vegetables and fruits.

37:18.800 --> 37:19.630
Don't just eat meat.

37:21.400 --> 37:22.480
Thank you, Dr. He.

37:23.710 --> 37:25.480
I don't know how to thank you enough.

37:25.760 --> 37:26.880
It's just my job.

37:31.840 --> 37:32.800
Congratulations.

37:33.280 --> 37:34.510
You got discharged so soon.

37:36.000 --> 37:37.760
When your hair grows back,

37:37.760 --> 37:39.190
take a photo

37:39.190 --> 37:40.320
and send it to me.

37:41.510 --> 37:44.590
Can you tell the lady who gave me this

37:45.760 --> 37:47.170
that I've been discharged?

37:47.750 --> 37:49.660
I'll let her know if I get the chance.

37:52.150 --> 37:53.710
Dr. He, we'll be going now.

37:54.630 --> 37:56.550
Thank you for everything you've done for us.

37:56.960 --> 37:57.960
I just did what I should.

37:59.280 --> 38:00.400
Say goodbye to Dr. He.

38:01.360 --> 38:02.070
Keep up the good work.

38:02.970 --> 38:03.700
You too, keep it up.

38:06.350 --> 38:06.990
Let's go.
